<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <link media="all" rel="stylesheet" href="./css/main.css">
    <title>Jaxboards - The free forum host</title>
    <meta property="og:title" content="Jaxboards - Free Forum Hosting" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="The last forum hosting you'll ever need." />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:image" content="/img/jax.svg" />
</head>

<body>
    <div id="container">
        <div id="logo"><a href="https://{{ domain }}">&nbsp;</a></div>

        {% apply spaceless %}
        <div id="bar">
            <a href="https://support.{{ domain }}" class="support">
                Support Forum
            </a>
            <a href="https://test.{{ domain }}" class="test">
                Test Forum
            </a>
            {# <a href="https://support.{{ domain }}" class="resource">
                Resources
            </a> #}
        </div>
        {% endapply %}

        <div id="content">
            <div class="box large">
                <div class="content flex" style="gap:20px">
                    <div class="flex-2">
                        <strong>So, you want a community. You've come to the right place.</strong>
                        <p>
                          Jaxboards is a forum software built from the ground up by humans, for humans.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                          It provides a sleek, lightweight platform to host your community.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                          <strong>We 💖 the Artisanal Web</strong> and aim to keep things small-scale, personal, and free of corporate influence. No algorithms, no monetization, no bots - just a platform to spend time with friends and have a good time.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div id="signup" class="flex-1">
                        <form method="post">
                            {% if error %}
                            <div class="error">{{ error }}</div>
                            {% endif %}
                            <input type="text" name="boardurl" id="boardname">.{{ domain }}<br>
                            <label for="username">Username:</label>
                            <input type="text" id="username" name="username" autocomplete="username"><br>
                            <label for="password">Password:</label>
                            <input type="password" id="password" name="password" autocomplete="new-password"><br>
                            <label for="email">Email:</label>
                            <input type="text" name="email" id="email" autocomplete="email"><br>
                            <input type="text" name="post" id="post">
                            <div class="center">
                                <input type="submit" name="submit" value="Register a Forum!">
                            </div>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="box mini box1">
                <div class="title">Customizable</div>
                <div class="content">
                  Jaxboards is incredibly easy to customize, and can be made to look exactly how
                  you want with just a few lines of CSS (and optionally HTML).
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="box mini box2">
                <div class="title">Stable &amp; Secure</div>
                <div class="content">
                    Jaxboards maintains the highest standards of efficient, optimized software
                    that can handle anything you throw at it, and a support forum that will back
                    you up 100%.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="box mini box3">
                <div class="title">Real Time!</div>
                <div class="content">
                    Everything that is posted, messaged,
                    or shared shows up instantly on the screen.<br><br>
                    Save your refresh button.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer id="copyright">
        Jaxboards &copy; 2007-{{ "now"|date("Y") }}, All Rights Reserved
    </footer>
</body>

</html>
